## Description
<a href="https://nuxtjs.org/">NuxtJS + VueJS</a> module for <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/@concepto/cli">Concepto DSL</a>

## Installation

```
$ npm install -g @concepto/nuxt
```

## Usage

```terminal
nuxt_dsl -s absolute_or_relative_file_to_compile.dsl
```
## Help:

```terminal
nuxt_dsl --help
```

